title: ​Registered Unemployed: September 2015 (NSO - National Statistics Office of Malta)
text: ( Source : NSO - National Statistics Office of Malta ) News2015_194 .indd 23 October 2015 | 1100 hrs | 194/2015 In September, the number of persons registering for work stood at 4,924 compared to 6,599 in the corresponding month last year.
